+/**
+ * calculate_clocksource_interval - Calculates a clocksource interval struct
+ *
+ * @c:		Pointer to clocksource.
+ * @adj:	Multiplyer adjustment.
+ * @length_nsec: Desired interval length in nanoseconds.
+ *
