+ *
+ * |HEAD          |
+ * |              |
+ * |prio_list.prev|<------------------------------------|
+ * |prio_list.next|<->|pl|<->|pl|<--------------->|pl|<-|
+ * |10            |   |10|   |21|   |21|   |21|   |40|   (prio)
+ * |              |   |  |   |  |   |  |   |  |   |  |
+ * |              |   |  |   |  |   |  |   |  |   |  |
